src_text: langutela lowu tirhiweke kahle lowu a wu rhangeriwile hi Komiti ya Vaholobye lowu seketeriweke hi Ntlawa wa Ntirho wa Xithekiniki Vafambisijeneral Yi tlhela yi tata ku khensa ka yona eka ntirho wa vatirhi vo huma eka SAPO, Ejensi ya swa Midende ya Vaakatiko ya Afrika-Dzonga (Sassa) na, tindzawulo ta Nhluvukiso wa Vaaki; Vukorhokeri bya Tiposo na Vuhlanganisi bya Tinqingho, Nkunguhato, Nandzeleriso na Nhlahluvo; Vutameri bya Nkwama wa Tiko; Vukorhokeri bya Maphorisa ya Afrika-Dzonga na GCI Khabinete yi khensa vavuyeriwa va midende hinkwavo eka ntirhisano wa vona hi nkarhi wa ku cinca loku Ku tlangeriwa ka dzana ra malembe ya Albertina Sisulu Khabinete yi hlamuseriwile hi malunghiselo yo tlangela lembexidzana ra Manana Albertina Sisulu loku nga ta va kona hi n hweti ya ku velekiwa ka yena, nhlangul Manana Sisulu u velekiwe hi ti 21 Nhlangula 1918, naswona Mutshamaxitulu wa IMC wa Ku Tlangela Lembexidzana, Holobye Jeff Radebe u kona laha ku andlala migingiriko leyi taka leyi fambelanaka na ku tlangeriwa ka lembexidzana Ku gweviwa ka tatana wa le Springs Khabinete yi amukela ku gweviwa ka wanuna wa muxanisi loyi a tiviwa swinene tanihi Xihovori xa le Spring U gweviwe kufikela eka malembe ya 35 ekhotsweni eka ku ringeta ku dlaya n wana wa yena wa jaha, ku xanisa n wana na ku tsan wa, xikan we na ku tirhisa na ku xavisa swidzidziharis Madzolonga lama simekiweke eka rimbewu ma ha ri ntlhontlho lowukulu emigangeni ya hina,tanihilaha swi tikombeke hakona hi mpfinyo lowu wa ha ku vaka kona wa n wana lontsongo evhengeleni ro xavisa swakudya leswi swekiweke na ku dyela ra Dros eSilverto
trg_text: Cabinet reiterates calls on law-enforcement authorities to leave no stone unturned in prosecuting perpetrators of these heinous crime It further calls on all of us to work together in stopping the violation of the rights of children and the most vulnerable members of our society Westbury protest Cabinet welcomes the intervention in Westbury by Police Minister Bheki Cele, which is part of the broader strategy to fight the scourge of drugs and gang-related violence in the are The intervention includes the deployment of the Tactical Response Team and a greater visible policing presenc Importantly, there will also be an investigation into allegations of corruption at the Westbury Police Statio Cabinet calls on the Westbury community and all communities to work with the police in ensuring that we root out acts of criminality, drugs and gangsters in their respective area 10.

src_text: Khabinete yi tshikelela xirhambo xa minhlangano ya nsindziso wa nawu ku tirha hi matimba swinene eka ku gweva vaendlamilandzu va vugevenga lebyi byo chavis Yi tlhela yi rhamba hinkwerhu ka hina ku tirhisana eka ku herisa ku tluriwa ka timfanelo ta vana na swirho leswi nga sirhelelekangiki swinene swa vaakatiko va hina Ku kombisa ku vilela ka le Westbury Khabinete yi amukela ku nghenelela ka Holobye wa Maphorisa Bheki Cele eWestbury, loku nga xiphemu xa qhinga ro angarhela ro lwisana na ntungu wa swidzidziharisi na madzolonga lama fambelanaka na mitlawa ya vugevenga eka ndhawu yoley Ku nghenelela ku katsa ku rhumeriwa ka Ntlawa wa Qhinga ro Angula (Tactical Response Team, va tlhela va tiveka tanihi Mabereta) na vukona bya maphorisa lebyi vonakaka swinen Xa nkoka swinene, hi leswaku ku ta tlhela ku va na vulavisisi bya swihehlo swa vukungundzwana eka Xitichi xa Maphorisa xa le Westbur Khabinete yi rhamba vaakatiko va le Westbury na vaaki hinkwavo ku tirhisana na maphorisa ku vona leswaku hi herisa migingiriko ya vugevenga, swidzidziharisi na mitlawa ya swigevenga eka tindhawu ta vona to hambanahamban Vugevenga1 Khabinete yi bumabumela tiejensi to sindzisa ku landzeleriwa ka nawu eka ku endla vulavisisi bya xiyimo xa le henhla lebyi fambelanaka na timhangu ta le timolo, mavhengele yo xavisa na tikereke ta MaIslam lebyi nga endla leswaku ku khomiwa vaehleketeriwa va khumekay A byi katsa Ntlawa wa Vululami, Nsivelo wa Vugevenga na Vusirheler Vaehleketeleriwa vanharhu va khomiwile hi mayelana na swibuluki eka ndhawu ya le Durban, ku katsa na Kereke ya MaIslam ya le Verula Vaehleketeleriwa hinkwavo va languteriwa ku langutana na swihehlo leswi katsaka ku dlaya na ku ringeta ku dlaya na tlula Nawu wa SwibulukiKhabinete yi tshembisa MaAfrika-Dzonga leswaku ku lwisana na vugevenga i xirhangana xa le henhla na leswaku mfumo wu ta ya emahlweni wu teka magoza lama faneleke ku vona leswaku ku na mbangu lowu hlayisekeke na ku sirheleleka eka vatshami hinkwavo va Afrika-Dzong Ku cinciwa ka vito: Makhanda1 Khabinete yi amukela ku cinciwa ka vito ra Grahamstown ri va Makhanda eKapa-Vuxa, hi ku xixima muphurofeta, mufilosofa na nhenha ya nyimpi ya Muqhoza leyi nga lwa na xikoloniKu cinca i xiphemu xa nkoka xa rendzo ra hina ra xidemokirasi naswona ku ta pfuneta ku tlakusa vun we bya vaaki hi lakukulu na ku aka ku tlangela ko enta ka ku avelana ka matimu ya hina Swiboho swa KhabineteKhabinete yi pasise modlolo wo korhokela lowu pfuxetiweke eka nsimeko wa Phurojeke ya Ndzhurho wa Vuhaxi byi ya eka Dijital Modlolo lowu wu amukela endlelo leri fambisiwaka hi makete/vuxavisi hi ku tirhisana swin we na vutirhisani na sekitara leyi nga riki ya mfumo na indhasitir Hi endlelo leri, mfumo wu nge he khumbeki eka nkumo wa Xibokisana xa Vuhaxi bya Mahungu vuhlayiselanhundzu, ku tleketliwa na ku nghenisiwa ka switirhisiwLeswi swi nyika Afrika-Dzonga nhluvukiso wo ya emakumu ka phurojeke hi ndlela leyi nghenisaka hinkwavo, yo kala yi nga durhi na ku koteka, naswona sweswo swi hungutaka nxungeto eka mfum Leswi swi ta susumeta ndzhurhiso wa ku vona ka dijitali ku ya eka 85% ya masungulo na ku yisa emahlweni, ku ya eka ku timiwa ka vuhaxi hinkwabyo bya analogKhabinete yi pasise Tsalwa ra Nkoka wa Swo Fana swa Afrika-Dzonga leri nga ta yisiwa eka Nhlangano wa Matiko (UN).
